==类似方法==
*[[Sono-Seq|Sono-Seq]]，与ChIP-Seq等同但略去了免疫沉淀的步骤。
*[[HITS-CLIP|HITS-CLIP]]<ref name="Licatalosi DD, Mele A, Fak JJ, et al. 2008 464–9">{{cite journal |author=Licatalosi DD, Mele A, Fak JJ, Ule J, Kayikci M, Chi SW, Clark TA, Schweitzer AC, Blume JE, Wang X, Darnell JC, Darnell RB. |title=HITS-CLIP yields genome-wide insights into brain alternative RNA processing |journal=Nature |volume=456 |issue=7221 |pages=464–9 |pmid=18978773 |pmc=2597294 |doi=10.1038/nature07488|date=November 2008}}</ref><ref>Darnell RB (2010) HITS-CLIP:  panoramic views of protein-RNA regulation in living cells.  Wiley Interdiscip Rev RNA. 1):266-86. doi: 10.1002/wrna.31 </ref>（亦被称为[[CLIP-Seq|CLIP-Seq]]），用于研究蛋白质与RNA而非DNA的关系。
*[[PAR-CLIP|PAR-CLIP]]，鉴定RNA结合蛋白（RBPs）的结合位点另一种方法。
*[[RIP-Chip|RIP-Chip]]，same goal and first steps, but does not use cross linking methods and uses microarray instead of sequencing
*[[Systematic_Evolution_of_Ligands_by_Exponential_Enrichment|SELEX]], a method for finding a consensus binding sequence
*[[Competition-ChIP|Competition-ChIP]], to measure relative replacement dynamics on DNA.
*[[ChiRP-Seq|ChiRP-Seq]]用于检测与RNA结合的DNA和蛋白质。
*[[ChIP-exo|ChIP-exo]] uses exonuclease treatment to achieve up to single base-pair resolution

